<body>
    <form action="/coimbatore" method="get">
    <div id="nav">
        <form action="/search" method="get">
          <p id="p1">Coimbatore</p>
         </form>
         <hr style="border-color:black;position:relative;top: 70px;">
         <div id="i1">
            <img id="apimg" src="https://images.thrillophilia.com/image/upload/s--rI05Fz1R--/c_fill,g_auto,h_600,q_auto,w_975/f_auto,fl_strip_profile/v1/images/photos/000/004/128/original/1597144988_shutterstock_1328746604.jpg.jpg">
        </div>
        <br><br><br><br><br>
        <div id="i2">
            <h2><strong><center>INFORMATION</center></strong></h2>
            <hr style="width: 950px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;"><br>
            <p>
                Coimbatore, also known as Kovai, is a bustling city located in the state of Tamil Nadu, India. It is renowned for its textile industry and is often referred to as the "Manchester of South India." Coimbatore offers a mix of modern amenities and natural beauty, making it an attractive destination for tourists. <br>

Best Time to Visit- October to March <br>
Ideal Vacation Duration-  2-3 days <br>
Average Vacation Cost:Starting from ₹25,000 (3 days/2 nights) <br>
Places to Visit-Marudamalai Temple: A popular Hindu temple dedicated to Lord Murugan, situated atop a hill offering scenic views.  <br>
Things to Do-Visit the Black Thunder Amusement Park: Enjoy a day of thrill and fun at one of the largest amusement parks in Asia. </p>
            
        </div>
        <div id="i3">
            <center><h2>WEATHER</h2></center><br>
            <hr style="width: 360px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;">
            <div class="icon">
                <h1><%=temp%>°C</h1><img src="/day/default.png" alt="" srcset="" id="image">
                </div>
                <h1 class="climate"><%=climate%></h1>
                <h2>Humidity : <%=humidity%>%<br><br>Wind Speed : <%=windspeed%>kmph</h2>
        </div>
        <div id="i4">
            <center><h2>TRANSPORTATION</h2></center><br>
            <hr style="width: 360px;height: 1.5px;background-color: black;"><br>
            <p> <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=oOAYqE64W2MO&format=png" height="25px" width="25px" alt="">&nbsp;&nbsp;By Air- Coimbatore International Airport is well-connected to major cities in India and abroad.<br><br>
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=d8MqKVWJkyqN&format=png" alt="" height="25px" width="25px">&nbsp;&nbsp; By Train- Coimbatore Junction is a major railway station with frequent trains from different parts of the country. <br><br>
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/?size=1x&id=f42OOoV1ACzO&format=png" alt="" height="25px" width="25px">&nbsp;&nbsp;By Road-  Coimbatore has excellent road connectivity with regular bus services from neighboring cities like Bangalore, Chennai, and Kochi.</p>
        </div>
    </form>
    <script>
        
        let image=document.getElementById("image");

        let climate=document.querySelector(".climate").textContent;
        if(climate=="Mist"){
            image.src="/day/Mist.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Patchy rain possible"){
            image.src="/day/Patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Moderate rain"){
            image.src="/day/Moderate.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light rain shower"){
            image.src="/day/patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Partly cloudy"){
            image.src="/day/default.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Cloudy"){
            image.src="/day/Cloudy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Overcast"){
            image.src="/day/Cloudy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Sunny"){
            image.src="/day/Sunny.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Clear"){
            image.src="/day/Sunny.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Thundery outbreaks possible"){
            image.src="/day/Thunderstorm.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Fog"){
            image.src="/day/Fog.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light rain"){
            image.src="/day/Patchy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Moderate or heavy rain shower"){
            image.src="/day/Heavy.png"
        }
        if(climate=="Light drizzle"){
            image.src="/day/Drizzle.png"
        }
    
</script>
